data.description: GOT IN-LAWS, COLLEGE KIDS, MULTIPLE FAMILIES, HOME BASED BUSINESS or NEED EXTRA INCOME? Come check out this Gorgeous Country Estate in BUCKINGHAM with a BEAUTIFUL NEWER GUEST HOUSE! Bring your animals and all your toys as this property is zoned Ag-2 and features a 40x60 barn with concrete floor, 50amp service and a 20x20 air-conditioned room. NO FLOOD ZONE, Metal roof, newer A/C, updated baths, vaulted ceilings, tile flooring, open floor plan and spacious pool area make it an easy place to call home. This well-built pool home sits on nearly 2 acres and has 6 bedrooms and 3 baths in the main house and a 1 bedroom 1 bath guest house. The main house kitchen features raised panel cabinets, stainless steel appliances, granite counters and a pantry. The 1st floor master bedroom has a large walk-in closet and a spacious bathroom. Sip your morning coffee on your lanai and enjoy the peace and quiet while you overlook your beautiful pool and pond. Your guests will never want to leave their GORGEOUS guest house that has 1-bedroom, living room, gourmet kitchen with granite, laundry area and a full bathroom. This house has everything you need and the outdoor space you have always wanted!
